==個人特色與投球風格==
*羅尼的主要武器為擁有均速95英哩以上的[[快速直球|快速直球]]，有時則可以投到100英哩，同時也擁有80多英哩的[[變速球|變速球]]，來混淆打者，並使其出局。<ref>[http://www.nytimes.com/2012/09/16/sports/baseball/pitcher-fernando-rodney-exceeds-tampa-bay-rays-expectations.html?_r=0 Rays Pitcher Wins Expectations Game]</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.baseballanalytics.org/baseball-analytics-blog/2013/5/19/the-fernando-rodney-difference.html |title=The Fernando Rodney Difference |access-date=2013-06-26 |archive-date=2014-08-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140821080032/http://www.baseballanalytics.org/baseball-analytics-blog/2013/5/19/the-fernando-rodney-difference.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

*此外，每一次救援成功後，羅尼都會擺出拉弓的姿勢來表達慶祝，並紀念在天上的父親來表達對其的思念。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.libertytimes.com.tw/2013/new/mar/21/today-sp2.htm |title=神箭闖江湖！羅德尼拉弓射箭「悼父」 |access-date=2013-06-26 |archive-date=2013-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130324221225/http://www.libertytimes.com.tw/2013/new/mar/21/today-sp2.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

